###  http://www.semanticweb.org/nicolas/ontologies/2021/8/patterns#StateMachineWohrer2020From
:StateMachineWohrer2020From rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                   :StateMachine ,
                   :Proposal ,
                   :General ,
